WEBVTT

00:01:54.200 --> 00:01:56.759
Your current condition is very unstable.

00:01:56.759 --> 00:01:59.360
Please minimize emotional fluctuations.

00:01:59.360 --> 00:02:01.800
Limit how often you go out.

00:02:01.800 --> 00:02:04.460
Avoid sudden deterioration of your condition.

00:02:10.680 --> 00:02:11.680
The doctor says

00:02:12.360 --> 00:02:14.820
we need to increase your medication dosage.

00:02:17.640 --> 00:02:18.700
I am a businessman.

00:02:18.960 --> 00:02:20.220
Finding good projects

00:02:20.520 --> 00:02:21.880
and good actors to work with

00:02:21.880 --> 00:02:23.120
is my job.

00:02:23.280 --> 00:02:24.840
Anything beyond that,

00:02:25.960 --> 00:02:27.490
I couldn't care less about.

00:02:35.800 --> 00:02:37.520
I'm sorry.

00:02:38.400 --> 00:02:40.440
I really want to tell you that

00:02:42.040 --> 00:02:43.760
I like you.

00:02:47.040 --> 00:02:48.240
I've said before,

00:02:48.240 --> 00:02:49.760
as long as you don't give up hope,

00:02:49.760 --> 00:02:51.690
there's still hope for the future.

00:02:52.280 --> 00:02:53.160
Shen Yifan,

00:02:53.400 --> 00:02:54.720
just you wait and see.

00:02:57.480 --> 00:02:58.680
I have someone I like.

00:02:59.760 --> 00:03:02.420
Miss Zheng truly has a passionate personality.

00:03:09.840 --> 00:03:11.500
Are you still in Switzerland?

00:03:12.800 --> 00:03:14.000
Help me find someone.

00:03:22.880 --> 00:03:23.480
Sweetie.

00:03:23.760 --> 00:03:24.720
Mommy's back.

00:03:30.880 --> 00:03:33.600
Mom, Dad and I have been waiting for you.

00:03:35.320 --> 00:03:36.240
Dad?

00:03:37.040 --> 00:03:37.760
Well...

00:03:38.680 --> 00:03:42.210
I just happened to run into him, so I kept him company for a while.

00:03:42.360 --> 00:03:43.760
Come here, sweetie.

00:03:47.920 --> 00:03:48.980
What are you doing?

00:03:49.600 --> 00:03:51.260
There's no such coincidence.

00:03:51.840 --> 00:03:53.520
Mom, don't be angry.

00:03:53.520 --> 00:03:56.320
I wanted Dad to play with me.

00:04:01.440 --> 00:04:03.570
If you want to play, I can play with you.

00:04:03.960 --> 00:04:06.000
And you can't just call someone Dad.

00:04:06.080 --> 00:04:06.810
Understand?

00:04:07.080 --> 00:04:09.600
But Mom, I really like Dad.

00:04:11.360 --> 00:04:12.480
Don't overthink it.

00:04:12.480 --> 00:04:14.410
I was just keeping the kid company.

00:04:17.959 --> 00:04:19.560
Thank you for your kindness.

00:04:20.120 --> 00:04:21.050
I appreciate it.

00:04:22.440 --> 00:04:24.360
I'll be going then.

00:04:43.240 --> 00:04:44.040
Mr. Shen.

00:04:44.680 --> 00:04:46.560
Your readings are much better today.

00:04:46.560 --> 00:04:50.159
Staying away from that annoying Zheng Ying was the right choice.

00:04:56.640 --> 00:04:58.040
But I don't feel good.

00:04:59.480 --> 00:05:00.160
Mr. Shen.

00:05:00.400 --> 00:05:01.560
Are you alright?

00:05:03.360 --> 00:05:05.020
What's on the schedule today?

00:05:05.480 --> 00:05:08.810
The variety show we discussed before starts filming today.

00:05:09.280 --> 00:05:10.610
I'll take her to the set.

00:05:10.640 --> 00:05:11.480
Mr. Shen.

00:05:12.520 --> 00:05:13.720
You don't need to go.

00:05:13.720 --> 00:05:14.520
Why not?

00:05:15.320 --> 00:05:16.360
Zheng Ying said

00:05:16.840 --> 00:05:18.440
you don't need to see her off.

00:05:27.360 --> 00:05:28.560
What else did she say?

00:05:28.720 --> 00:05:30.440
We're just business partners.

00:05:30.440 --> 00:05:32.900
Why are you still so involved in my business?

00:05:33.080 --> 00:05:33.680
By the way,

00:05:33.880 --> 00:05:35.280
that line is really good.

00:05:35.480 --> 00:05:36.080
This line

00:05:36.120 --> 00:05:37.840
was specially added by our scriptwriter

00:05:37.840 --> 00:05:39.280
and it's the key moment

00:05:39.280 --> 00:05:40.400
in today's filming.

00:05:40.400 --> 00:05:42.060
We're aiming to trend online.

00:05:43.280 --> 00:05:43.610
Good.

00:05:43.920 --> 00:05:45.080
You two go over your lines again.

00:05:45.080 --> 00:05:46.440
We'll start shooting soon.

00:05:46.440 --> 00:05:46.880
Okay.

