These game-based variety shows are

00:05:53.080 --> 00:05:54.200
extremely popular now.

00:05:54.200 --> 00:05:55.930
We must do a good job recording.

00:05:56.120 --> 00:05:56.920
Recording...

00:05:58.760 --> 00:05:59.440
Hey!

00:06:00.080 --> 00:06:01.600
What's wrong with you?

00:06:02.080 --> 00:06:03.600
At yesterday's film festival,

00:06:03.600 --> 00:06:06.560
you were the center of attention as a new actress.

00:06:07.040 --> 00:06:07.720
How come

00:06:07.920 --> 00:06:09.720
after trending for just a few hours,

00:06:09.720 --> 00:06:11.650
you're already acting like a diva?

00:06:12.400 --> 00:06:13.400
Diva...

00:06:16.760 --> 00:06:18.890
Weren't you supposed to be the hunter?

00:06:18.960 --> 00:06:21.000
But you look more like the prey to me.

00:06:22.000 --> 00:06:22.680
Prey...

00:06:24.040 --> 00:06:25.100
If you keep this up,

00:06:25.120 --> 00:06:27.320
I'm going to complain to Director Shen.

