This is basically her state right now.

00:06:41.720 --> 00:06:42.960
But the crew is very satisfied.

00:06:42.960 --> 00:06:44.200
They say she's very cooperative.

00:06:44.200 --> 00:06:46.520
Whatever the crew asks, she films it.

00:06:46.760 --> 00:06:47.760
Nonsense.

00:06:48.720 --> 00:06:50.400
Should we help her?

00:06:51.680 --> 00:06:52.280
No need.

00:06:54.000 --> 00:06:55.530
She needs time to calm down.

00:06:55.920 --> 00:06:57.400
They're playing games today.

00:06:57.400 --> 00:06:58.960
Losers get thrown into the water.

00:06:58.960 --> 00:07:00.720
She volunteered to go into the water

00:07:00.720 --> 00:07:02.780
and wouldn't let Wan Yuchen help her.

00:07:03.360 --> 00:07:04.290
How ridiculous.

00:07:06.120 --> 00:07:07.600
Should we go check on her?

00:07:08.120 --> 00:07:09.250
What's there to see?

00:07:09.800 --> 00:07:11.400
Have you finished your work?

00:07:17.960 --> 00:07:18.720
Mr. Shen.

00:07:19.080 --> 00:07:21.520
Wan Yuchen said she was doing an escape room game

00:07:21.520 --> 00:07:23.320
and volunteered to chase after a non-player character,

00:07:23.320 --> 00:07:25.480
but then a prop fell and injured her.

00:07:25.960 --> 00:07:26.720
What?

00:07:27.040 --> 00:07:27.970
She got injured.

00:07:34.480 --> 00:07:35.840
This photo of yours

00:07:36.159 --> 00:07:38.000
looks so fake.

00:07:45.440 --> 00:07:47.159
How about this? Real enough for you?

00:07:47.159 --> 00:07:48.090
Take it quickly.

00:07:48.400 --> 00:07:50.400
I really don't understand why I'm not sleeping at this hour

00:07:50.400 --> 00:07:52.930
and accompanying you with all this nonsense.

00:07:54.000 --> 00:07:56.360
Hiking up mountains, going into water.

00:07:56.520 --> 00:07:58.720
And now pretending to be injured?

00:07:59.600 --> 00:08:01.680
All this effort to play the victim,

00:08:01.680 --> 00:08:03.810
who exactly are you trying to impress?

00:08:06.840 --> 00:08:07.760
Is it that person?

00:08:07.760 --> 00:08:08.720
Shut your mouth

00:08:08.720 --> 00:08:10.040
and stop gossiping about me.

00:08:10.040 --> 00:08:10.840
Otherwise...

00:08:15.800 --> 00:08:16.200
Here.

00:08:24.880 --> 00:08:27.800
You know who I'll send this to.

00:09:05.000 --> 00:09:06.640
It's been hours

00:09:07.000 --> 00:09:08.400
and he still hasn't come.

00:09:13.080 --> 00:09:15.560
Does he think I'm not injured badly enough?

00:09:16.720 --> 00:09:18.560
This cold-hearted man.

00:09:26.200 --> 00:09:27.800
Master Zhou says

00:09:28.200 --> 00:09:31.280
a martial artist shouldn't mind this little pain.

00:09:37.760 --> 00:09:39.120
Self-harm

00:09:39.120 --> 00:09:40.780
is absolutely unacceptable.

00:09:41.320 --> 00:09:42.840
I'd better call and ask.

00:09:51.840 --> 00:09:52.560
Hello,

00:09:52.640 --> 00:09:53.360
Shen Yifan.

00:09:53.800 --> 00:09:54.680
Where are you now?

00:09:54.680 --> 00:09:55.320
I...

00:09:55.840 --> 00:09:57.760
I'm in my room at the film set.

00:09:57.840 --> 00:09:58.640
Wait for me.

00:09:58.840 --> 00:09:59.970
I'll be right there.

00:10:05.080 --> 00:10:06.200
I knew it.

00:10:06.360 --> 00:10:07.820
He would definitely come.

00:11:17.320 --> 00:11:18.200
You're here.

00:11:20.680 --> 00:11:21.480
Come here.

00:11:22.120 --> 00:11:23.650
What kind of person are you?

00:11:24.360 --> 00:11:25.720
I'm injured

00:11:25.720 --> 00:11:27.320
and you won't even help me up.

00:11:32.120 --> 00:11:34.180
I guess I'll walk over by myself then.

00:11:56.520 --> 00:11:58.520
You haven't been to the set for days.

00:11:58.680 --> 00:11:59.940
Why did you come today?

00:12:00.120 --> 00:12:01.850
Didn't you say you were injured

00:12:01.880 --> 00:12:03.410
and asked me to come see you?

00:12:03.800 --> 00:12:04.600
Yes.

00:12:04.720 --> 00:12:07.920
I'm injured. It really hurts.

00:12:13.080 --> 00:12:16.140
Someone who's injured wouldn't be wearing high heels.

00:12:21.120 --> 00:12:22.450
What do you want from me?

00:12:24.160 --> 00:12:25.080
Nothing.

00:12:25.880 --> 00:12:28.120
I just haven't seen you for days

00:12:28.320 --> 00:12:29.580
and I miss you a little.

00:12:31.800 --> 00:12:33.960
At the film festival opening ceremony,

00:12:33.960 --> 00:12:35.400
I made myself very clear.

00:12:36.760 --> 00:12:37.920
I know.

00:12:38.280 --> 00:12:39.360
Your position

00:12:39.360 --> 00:12:41.400
is perfectly clear to me.

00:12:41.920 --> 00:12:42.920
But,

00:12:43.160 --> 00:12:44.400
just as I can't

00:12:44.400 --> 00:12:46.040
force you to like me,

00:12:46.400 --> 00:12:48.880
you can't stop me from liking you either.

00:12:51.840 --> 00:12:53.200
I think you're doing the right thing.

00:12:53.200 --> 00:12:54.760
Just keep going like this.

00:12:54.840 --> 00:12:56.560
If you persist a little longer,

00:12:56.560 --> 00:12:58.080
you'll complete your plan

00:12:58.120 --> 00:12:59.280
and we can leave.

00:13:01.960 --> 00:13:03.760
What if I can't hold on anymore?

00:13:09.160 --> 00:13:10.690
I find that the harder I try,

00:13:13.840 --> 00:13:15.300
the more I can't let her go.

00:13:19.560 --> 00:13:21.480
I truly like you.

00:13:22.240 --> 00:13:23.560
You may be perfect,

00:13:23.800 --> 00:13:25.400
but I'm pretty great too.

00:13:25.960 --> 00:13:26.840
So,

00:13:27.000 --> 00:13:29.560
you really need to think about this carefully.

00:13:29.560 --> 00:13:32.220
What if you end up missing out on someone like me,

00:13:32.480 --> 00:13:34.560
who's smart and beautiful?

00:13:34.760 --> 00:13:37.360
You won't even have a chance to regret it later.

00:13:39.880 --> 00:13:41.480
I don't want to have regrets.

00:13:42.960 --> 00:13:44.620
I don't want to miss out on her.

00:13:51.880 --> 00:13:54.610
I want to throw caution to the wind just this once.

00:14:07.440 --> 00:14:09.800
Since you're being so stubborn,

00:14:09.880 --> 00:14:11.340
then I'll... listen to me.

00:14:14.880 --> 00:14:15.840
So no matter what,

00:14:15.840 --> 00:14:17.970
I can't stop you from liking me, right?

00:14:19.920 --> 00:14:20.720
Fine.

00:14:21.440 --> 00:14:22.440
Then listen to me.

00:14:23.200 --> 00:14:25.440
I'm willing to use all my resources to build you up.

00:14:25.440 --> 00:14:27.160
And I'm in a hurry to make you famous

00:14:27.160 --> 00:14:29.560
because I have a congenital heart disease.

00:14:31.400 --> 00:14:32.360
Before long,

00:14:33.400 --> 00:14:34.440
I'll be dead.

00:14:36.920 --> 00:14:37.980
Are you scared now?

00:14:39.600 --> 00:14:40.560
This is who I am.

00:14:42.440 --> 00:14:43.570
Do you still like me?

00:14:44.600 --> 00:14:46.000
Do you dare to like me now?

00:15:08.480 --> 00:15:10.480
After all this nonsense,

00:15:10.600 --> 00:15:11.880
I'm getting hungry.

00:15:12.520 --> 00:15:14.250
Want to go get something to eat?

00:15:23.920 --> 00:15:24.840
He's sick

00:15:25.040 --> 00:15:26.970
with only a few months left to live.

00:15:27.320 --> 00:15:28.320
Shen Yifan,

00:15:28.680 --> 00:15:30.680
how dare you make up such a lie!

00:15:31.080 --> 00:15:31.880
[Yan A·222U5]

00:15:33.760 --> 00:15:35.880
Do you think you're a screenwriter making up stories?

00:15:35.880 --> 00:15:37.440
Even if you were writing fiction,

00:15:37.440 --> 00:15:39.000
I haven't seen such

00:15:39.000 --> 00:15:40.930
clichéd plots in nearly ten years.

00:15:41.120 --> 00:15:42.080
Shen Yifan,

00:15:42.800 --> 00:15:44.280
you big liar!

00:15:45.560 --> 00:15:46.520
Liar!

00:15:55.040 --> 00:15:57.440
How's that investigation I asked you to do?

00:15:57.520 --> 00:15:59.240
About Shen Yifan you asked me to look into,

00:15:59.240 --> 00:16:02.080
he's practically a legend in the investment world.

00:16:02.080 --> 00:16:04.080
I heard he was a child prodigy,

00:16:04.120 --> 00:16:04.960
with an extremely high IQ.

00:16:04.960 --> 00:16:05.720
Mr. Zhou,

00:16:05.880 --> 00:16:08.400
let's skip these details about Mr. Shen.

00:16:08.720 --> 00:16:10.320
Focus on other aspects.

00:16:10.960 --> 00:16:12.160
Other aspects?

00:16:12.440 --> 00:16:14.960
Like any weaknesses, for example.

00:16:15.520 --> 00:16:16.120
There aren't any.

00:16:16.120 --> 00:16:17.080
There must be.

00:16:18.040 --> 00:16:18.840
Keep digging.

00:16:21.640 --> 00:16:22.560
That 'Drunken Jade Mountain' project,

00:16:22.560 --> 00:16:24.960
the writing team we found is quite efficient.

00:16:24.960 --> 00:16:27.160
I didn't expect them to deliver the adaptation plan so quickly.

00:16:27.160 --> 00:16:29.400
Send it to Yiping Sunshine for approval as soon as possible,

00:16:29.400 --> 00:16:30.440
then keep an eye on the writing team

00:16:30.440 --> 00:16:31.720
to produce an outline quickly.

00:16:31.720 --> 00:16:32.920
No problem.

00:16:33.160 --> 00:16:34.520
If things continue to go this smoothly,

00:16:34.520 --> 00:16:36.040
I believe it won't be long

00:16:36.040 --> 00:16:37.440
before we see the script

00:16:37.440 --> 00:16:38.560
and start filming.

00:16:38.560 --> 00:16:39.200
In that case,

00:16:39.200 --> 00:16:42.060
we'll be one big step closer to completing our plan.

00:16:44.080 --> 00:16:45.920
There are too many unpredictable factors.

00:16:45.920 --> 00:16:47.520
Let's push forward quickly.

00:16:48.240 --> 00:16:50.300
How's the variety show coming along?

00:16:53.160 --> 00:16:56.200
Why would anyone ship us together?

00:16:57.080 --> 00:16:58.720
A couple pairing can be unpopular,

00:16:58.720 --> 00:17:00.520
but this is just bizarre.

00:17:04.640 --> 00:17:05.240
Director,

00:17:05.240 --> 00:17:06.760
this is truly a heaven-sent opportunity.

00:17:06.760 --> 00:17:07.359
Look.

00:17:07.760 --> 00:17:09.079
If we can capture more footage

00:17:09.079 --> 00:17:10.760
of their interactions,

00:17:10.760 --> 00:17:12.359
we'll have our trending topic.

00:17:12.359 --> 00:17:13.319
With a hot topic,

00:17:13.319 --> 00:17:14.319
our show's popularity

00:17:14.319 --> 00:17:15.250
will skyrocket.

00:17:15.440 --> 00:17:16.839
Mr. Shen clearly stated

00:17:16.839 --> 00:17:18.480
not to hype up romantic relationships.

00:17:18.480 --> 00:17:20.880
We just won't do it openly, problem solved.

00:17:22.560 --> 00:17:25.440
What if they really shoot it this way?

00:17:25.640 --> 00:17:26.599
What will we do?

00:17:42.800 --> 00:17:45.000
Now, you two need to figure out a way

00:17:45.000 --> 00:17:46.800
to eat the peanuts in your plates.

00:17:46.800 --> 00:17:48.330
Both of you need to eat them.

00:17:57.800 --> 00:17:58.520
Look.

00:18:08.240 --> 00:18:09.320
I got it! I ate it!

00:18:10.760 --> 00:18:11.520
Yuchen,

00:18:11.800 --> 00:18:13.480
Zhengying seems a bit cold now.

00:18:13.480 --> 00:18:15.600
Shouldn't you take off your jacket

00:18:15.600 --> 00:18:16.600
and give it to her?

00:18:21.240 --> 00:18:23.720
