What exactly are you trying to do?

00:21:28.640 --> 00:21:30.560
My neck doesn't feel right.

00:21:30.960 --> 00:21:32.420
I think I slept on it wrong.

00:21:32.720 --> 00:21:33.400
That neck.

00:21:36.760 --> 00:21:38.360
Some heart disease patients

00:21:38.360 --> 00:21:40.760
may develop enlargement

00:21:40.760 --> 00:21:42.220
of their fingers and toes,

00:21:42.320 --> 00:21:44.600
with nails that bulge like drumsticks.

00:21:48.200 --> 00:21:50.520
I've been learning the I Ching from Wan Yuchen lately.

00:21:50.520 --> 00:21:51.650
I can read palms now.

00:21:51.720 --> 00:21:52.920
Want me to read yours?

00:21:53.160 --> 00:21:54.220
Great, you agreed.

00:22:04.200 --> 00:22:05.440
Is this palm reading

00:22:06.480 --> 00:22:08.440
or are you just taking advantage of me?

00:22:08.440 --> 00:22:10.370
I'm definitely taking advantage.

00:22:10.600 --> 00:22:12.400
Of course I'm reading your palm.

00:22:14.160 --> 00:22:15.240
All done.

00:22:15.360 --> 00:22:16.220
Nothing wrong.

00:22:18.120 --> 00:22:19.520
You still haven't told me

00:22:19.760 --> 00:22:21.890
why you've really come back this time.

00:22:23.240 --> 00:22:24.900
What could I possibly be up to?

00:22:25.120 --> 00:22:27.480
What kind of trouble were you expecting?

00:22:27.800 --> 00:22:28.320
Well,

00:22:28.320 --> 00:22:31.380
if there's nothing else, I'll head back to the film set.

00:22:45.080 --> 00:22:45.720
Hello?

00:22:47.880 --> 00:22:48.960
Yes, it's me.

00:22:49.720 --> 00:22:50.920
The production team.

00:22:58.120 --> 00:23:00.160
I knew he wasn't really sick.

00:23:01.040 --> 00:23:02.040
Seriously.

00:23:03.600 --> 00:23:04.960
Then why did he lie to me?

00:23:11.680 --> 00:23:12.280
Mr. Cheng.

00:23:12.720 --> 00:23:13.400
What is it?

00:23:13.400 --> 00:23:14.240
Zheng Ying.

00:23:15.000 --> 00:23:17.720
I regret to tell you some bad news.

00:23:17.840 --> 00:23:19.320
Your boss, Shen Yifan,

00:23:19.760 --> 00:23:22.240
has a serious heart condition.

00:23:22.840 --> 00:23:25.320
I don't think he's right for you.

00:23:26.960 --> 00:23:27.920
What?

00:23:28.680 --> 00:23:30.960
To make me believe he's really sick,

00:23:31.120 --> 00:23:33.200
now you're also lying to me with him.

00:23:36.360 --> 00:23:36.840
Hey.

00:23:46.760 --> 00:23:48.560
If I want to stay by her side,

00:23:48.560 --> 00:23:50.290
I need to figure something out.

00:23:51.840 --> 00:23:52.480
Linda.

00:23:53.880 --> 00:23:55.080
Mr. Cheng, what is it?

00:23:56.240 --> 00:23:58.200
Notify the home gym

00:23:58.320 --> 00:24:00.520
I'm starting to work out today.

00:24:01.080 --> 00:24:02.410
Have the trainer ready.

00:24:02.920 --> 00:24:03.720
Go ahead.

00:24:05.600 --> 00:24:06.260
Zheng Ying.

00:24:07.360 --> 00:24:07.960
You left the production team

00:24:07.960 --> 00:24:09.240
without notifying Yu Youyi or me,

00:24:09.240 --> 00:24:10.480
on your own.

00:24:10.920 --> 00:24:12.960
And the production team called saying

00:24:12.960 --> 00:24:15.080
you're not following the script at all.

00:24:15.080 --> 00:24:15.640
Why?

00:24:17.000 --> 00:24:18.560
Because I hate lying

00:24:18.960 --> 00:24:20.820
and I hate being lied to even more.

00:24:23.080 --> 00:24:25.240
What was my purpose in taking this show?

00:24:25.240 --> 00:24:27.160
Wasn't it to distinguish myself from being just an actress

00:24:27.160 --> 00:24:28.520
and show my true self?

00:24:28.520 --> 00:24:29.560
You're too naive.

00:24:29.960 --> 00:24:31.200
No reality show

00:24:31.200 --> 00:24:32.760
can be completely authentic.

00:24:32.760 --> 00:24:33.720
And no one

00:24:33.720 --> 00:24:34.640
can be completely themselves

00:24:34.640 --> 00:24:35.880
in front of cameras.

00:24:36.240 --> 00:24:38.360
Fans can edit and ship however they want,

00:24:38.360 --> 00:24:39.640
that's their freedom.

00:24:39.840 --> 00:24:40.680
But I absolutely will not

00:24:40.680 --> 00:24:42.080
cater to some show effect

00:24:42.080 --> 00:24:43.800
by deliberately misleading them.

00:24:43.800 --> 00:24:44.400
After all,

00:24:44.840 --> 00:24:45.880
fake is fake,

00:24:45.880 --> 00:24:48.340
and lies will always be exposed eventually.

00:24:51.640 --> 00:24:52.900
I know everything now,

00:24:53.200 --> 00:24:55.280
so you don't need to deceive me

00:24:55.280 --> 00:24:57.040
by pretending to be a heart patient

00:24:57.040 --> 00:24:59.480
and getting others to help you lie to me.

00:24:59.880 --> 00:25:01.340
Is it really that serious?

00:25:02.120 --> 00:25:04.040
Shen Yifan, I just want to ask you,

00:25:04.040 --> 00:25:06.100
why did you lie to me about being sick?

00:25:06.520 --> 00:25:07.920
What was the real reason?

00:25:11.280 --> 00:25:12.120
Shen Yifan.

00:25:14.000 --> 00:25:15.880
You never liked me,

00:25:17.480 --> 00:25:18.280
did you?

00:25:28.920 --> 00:25:29.760
Shen Yifan.

00:25:31.720 --> 00:25:34.920
Wasn't there even one moment when you had feelings for me?

00:25:35.040 --> 00:25:36.040
Just say there was.

00:25:36.040 --> 00:25:36.880
No.

00:25:39.160 --> 00:25:40.480
How is that possible?

00:25:40.560 --> 00:25:41.320
You clearly...

00:25:41.320 --> 00:25:41.980
Zheng Ying,

00:25:43.720 --> 00:25:46.050
I've never had romantic feelings for you.

00:25:46.560 --> 00:25:47.920
I never, never,

00:25:47.920 --> 00:25:49.640
never liked you that way.

00:26:07.640 --> 00:26:09.000
If my feelings

00:26:09.440 --> 00:26:11.100
make you this uncomfortable,

00:26:12.600 --> 00:26:13.930
then I'd rather give up.

00:26:15.960 --> 00:26:17.320
I was wrong before.

00:26:18.400 --> 00:26:20.840
I shouldn't have kept pursuing you

00:26:21.200 --> 00:26:22.930
after you clearly rejected me.

00:26:25.760 --> 00:26:26.680
From now on,

00:26:27.360 --> 00:26:27.920
we'll just be

00:26:27.920 --> 00:26:30.250
in a normal boss-employee relationship.

00:26:31.760 --> 00:26:33.360
I won't cross the line again.

00:26:38.000 --> 00:26:39.320
But I should warn you,

00:26:39.960 --> 00:26:40.960
I won't be able

00:26:40.960 --> 00:26:43.420
to get over my feelings for you that quickly.

00:26:43.480 --> 00:26:44.280
So,

00:26:44.600 --> 00:26:45.680
I might still get drunk

00:26:45.680 --> 00:26:47.010
and call you sometimes.

00:26:48.840 --> 00:26:50.370
Just do what you did before -

00:26:50.600 --> 00:26:52.040
ignore me completely.

00:26:53.640 --> 00:26:55.000
Or be kind enough

00:26:55.640 --> 00:26:57.240
to call Yu Youyi to pick me up.

